{"per_page":10,"total":5,"current":1,"data":[{"title":"2017年的回顾","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>2017年，我经历了什么？</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/2017-Annual-Summary","categories":["Dailylife"]},{"title":"Bit-Computing","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>位运算是对内存中的数据(二进制数据)直接进行二进制运算操作</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/Bit-Computing","categories":["ComputerScience","位运算"]},{"title":"Beego Framework","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>方便开发 Go Web 应用的开源框架</p>\n<p>文档地址:<a href=\"https://beego.me/docs/intro/\" target=\"_blank\">https://beego.me/docs/intro</a></p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/BeeGo","categories":["ComputerScience","Go"]},{"title":"App 上架流程","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>App 的 上架 和 真机测试，算是App开发流程的最后一步了，那么苹果是如何保证 App Store 上 App 的安全性，以及本地真机测试时苹果是如何授权的呢？</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/AppAddAppStore","categories":["ComputerScience","iOS"]},{"title":"CocosCreator本地储存 - cc.sys.localStorage","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>在CocosCreator中，本地储存我们常用cc.sys.localStorage来完成。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>其提供了三种常用方法：</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li><code>cc.sys.localStorage.setItem(key, value)</code></li>\n<li><code>cc.sys.localStorage.getItem(key)</code></li>\n<li><code>cc.sys.localStorage.removeItem(key)</code></li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/CocosCreator_LocalStorage","categories":["CocosCreator","ComputerScience","Game"]},{"title":"Apple Push Notification service","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>APNs : Apple Push Notification service 的简称，由苹果公司提供的推送通知服务</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/ApplePushNotification","categories":["ComputerScience","iOS"]},{"title":"计算机原理简介","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>计算机是由层次结构组成的，每层完成规定的功能。</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/ComputerScienceBase","categories":["ComputerScience"]},{"title":"让自己的开源库支持CocoaPods","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>在iOS开发中，CocoaPods几乎成了使用第三方库的标配工具，因此我们也可以让自己的公共库也支持CocoaPods。</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/CreateLibToCocoaPod","categories":["ComputerScience","iOS"]},{"title":"计算机科学 - 二进制和算数逻辑单元","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>现代的计算机和依赖计算机的设备里都用到二进制,而算术逻辑单元主要功能是进行二进制的算术运算。</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/ComputerScience_ALU","categories":["ComputerScience"]},{"title":"数据结构","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p><strong>数据结构是计算机中存储、组织数据的方式。</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>数据结构可透过编程语言所提供的数据类型、引用及其他操作加以实现。一个设计良好的数据结构，应该在尽可能使用较少的时间与空间资源的前提下，支持各种程序运行。</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/DataStructure","categories":["ComputerScience"]}]}